premise_source_doc_sentence: Central America consists of seven countries : Belize , Costa Rica , El Salvador , Guatemala , Honduras , Nicaragua , and Panama .
Central America is a part of the Mesoamerican biodiversity hotspot , which extends from northern Guatemala through to central Panama .

From 1609 until 1821 , most of the territory within Central America -- except for the lands that would become Belize and Panama -- was governed by the Viceroyalty of New Spain from Mexico City as the Captaincy General of Guatemala .

Panama  (  -LSB- ˈpænəmɑː -RSB- ; Panamá -LSB- panaˈma -RSB-  )  , officially called the Republic of Panama  (  República de Panamá  )  , is a country usually considered to be entirely in North America or Central America .
For two brief periods he was head of state of the State of El Salvador , within the Federal Republic of Central America  (  1839 and 1840  )  .
The Panama Canal is the connection of Central America with the rest world , and the main means of communication for trade with Central America , South America , United States , Europe and Asia .
Panama is recognized as the most industrial country in Central America , and the second in Latin America after Chile .
